snippet.title: Max Downforce (2)
snippet.description:
This second gameplay video shows the original 'Forest' track in Max Downforce version 1.1.0. This new version of my Love2d pseudo 3d racing game features a second track as well as dual stick gamepad support. In this video the game is played with the gamepad.

Game download page:
https://gamejolt.com/games/max_downforce/286316
